On 11/9/03 12:40 PM, "Kent" <kenth415(-at-)yahoo.com> wrote:

> Now, my question is, where does
> should this lose wire go? I can run a length of wire
> up to the front, but where to from there?

The lose wire leaves the gas tank compartment and meets with a plastic
insulating connector. From there it goes up to the front and connects behind
the dash at the gas gauge.

> I looked in the archives but couldn't find the answer,
